
position

相對定位

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
     </head>
     <body  style="height:1500px;">
         <!--position-->
         <hi>css教學</hi>
         <div style="position:relative; top:10px; width:80px;height:80px; background-color:blue;"></div>
         <div style="width:120px;height:120px;background-color:red;"></div>




     </body>


 
</html>




絕對定位前



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
     </head>
     <body  style="height:1500px;">
         <!--position-->
         <hi>css教學</hi>
         <div style="position:relative; top:10px; width:80px;height:80px; background-color:blue;"></div>
         <div style="width:120px;height:120px;background-color:red;"></div>


         <br/>
         <div style="padding:30px; border:5px solid red">
              <div style="padding:30px; border:5px solid red;">
                  <div style="width:40px; height:40px; background-color:blue;">
               </div>
              </div>
     </body>


 
</html>




絕對定位後

相對於獨立一層(飄起來
(外層div設定定位後會根據外層做定位)

       會不知道有這層      <div style=" position:absolute;width:40px; height:40px; background-color:blue;">







<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
     </head>
     <body  style="height:1500px;">
         <!--position-->
         <hi>css教學</hi>
         <div style="position:relative; top:10px; width:80px;height:80px; background-color:blue;"></div>
         <div style="width:120px;height:120px;background-color:red;"></div>


         <br/>
         <div style="padding:30px; border:5px solid red">
              <div style="padding:30px; border:5px solid red;">
                  <div style=" position:absolute;width:40px; height:40px; background-color:blue;">
               </div>
              </div>
     </body>


 
</html>



opacity& border-radius
透明度調整


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
     </head>
     <body  style="height:1500px;">
         <!--opacity&border-radius-->
         <hi>css教學</hi>
         <p style="position:relative;top :65px: left:25px;>">你好</p>
         <div style="opacity:0.5;width:80px;height:80px;background-color:rgb(27, 74, 194);"></div>


        
     </body>


 
</html>






border-radius



圓弧度調整
每個角都可以改
20px 30px 40px 20px
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
     </head>
     <body  style="height:1500px;">
         <!--opacity&border-radius-->
         <hi>css教學</hi>
         <p style="position:relative;top :65px: left:25px;>">你好</p>
         <div style="opacity:0.5;border-radius:10px;width:80px;height:80px;background-color:rgb(27, 74, 194);"></div>


        
     </body>


 
</html>



css顏色另一個寫法



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
            <style>
             p{
               color:blue;
             }

            </style>
     </head>
     <body 
         <!--css另一種寫法-->
         <hi>css教學</hi>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>


        
     </body>


 
</html>




如何引入css檔案




好處是網頁頁面多可以直接套用
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
           <!--引入css檔案-->
           <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
     </head>
     <body>
         
         <h1>css教學</h1>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>
         <p >新年快樂</p>


        
     </body>


 
</html>




p{
    color:blue;
    background-color:grey;
  }
  h1{
     color:red;
  }





class&id
class用.
id用#

標籤做分類

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
       
           <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
     </head>
     <body>
         <!--class&id-->
         <h1>css教學</h1>
         <p class="food">壽司</p>
         <p class="food background-grey">牛排</p>
         <p class="food">拉麵</p>
         <p class="language background-grey">英文</p>
         <p class="language">中文</p>
         <p class="language">拉丁文</p>


        
     </body>


 
</html>

.food{
    color:red;
}



.language{
    color:blue;
}



.background-grey{
    background-color:grey;
}


id給唯一識別名稱

id一個名字只能出現一次

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
       
           <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
     </head>
     <body>
         <!--class&id-->
         <h1 id="css-h1">css教學</h1>
         <p class="food">壽司</p>
         <p class="food background-grey">牛排</p>
         <p class="food">拉麵</p>
         <p class="language background-grey">英文</p>
         <p class="language">中文</p>
         <p class="language">拉丁文</p>


        
     </body>


 
</html>

.food{
    color:red;
}



.language{
    color:blue;
}



.background-grey{
    background-color:grey;
}



#css-h1{
    color:yellow;
    background-color:grey;
}





css選擇器
w3school selector


ul li{
    background-color: grey;
}
找尋ul中li類別更改


ul a{
    background-color: grey;
}

找尋ul中a類別更改





#id-1, .class-1{
    background-color: grey;
}
套用



[type]{
    background-color: grey;
}
套用在有type屬性的標籤上


[href]{
    background-color: grey;
}

套用在有href屬性的標籤上



h1:hover{
    background-color: grey;
}

滑鼠滑過h1標籤時背景就會變成灰色



[type]:hover{
    background-color: grey;
}


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
            <title>W的網頁</title>
       
           <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
     </head>
     <body>
         <!--更多套用css方法-->
         <h1 >css教學</h1>
         <p class="class-1">這是一個段落</p>
         <p class="class-1">這是第二個段落</p>
         <h2 id="id-1">你好啊 </h2>
         <h2> 安安你好啊</h2>
         <ul>
               <li><a href="https://www.google.com.tw/">google</a></li>
               <li>facebook</li>
               <li>ig</li>

         </ul>
         <input type="text"/>
         <br/>
         <input type="password" />

        
     </body>


 
</html>
